    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @davidpike7, I just did some more fixes on the toggle widget, can you this build on your website: https://gist.githubusercontent.com/vvo/19d16de5d738ab55eaa3a9e1e3c7b67b/raw/71ff01360b6591186142b1457d5add5f40f746a3/instantsearch.min.js\n\nHere's what's new:\n\n```\nfeat(toggle): Provide a better default widget\n\nThis update brings:\n- default to showing the next user action items count instead of the\ncurrent number of displayed hits\n\nwhich means:\nif checkbox is not checked, show: [ ] free shipping (countWhenChecked)\nif checkbox is checked, show: [x] free shipping (countWhenNotChecked)\n- fix numeric based on and off values (fixes #1096)\n- provide `onFacetValue` and `offFacetValue` template data, fixes #919\n```\n",
